Package: genepopedit
Title: Functions to Manipulate Genepop SNP Datasets.
Version: 1.0
Description: A simple and flexible tool for manipulating large multi-locus datasets in R.
    Using data structured according to 'Genepop' format (http://genepop.curtin.edu.au/),
    these functions provide a flexible and code-based approach to remove manipulate, convert,
    and subsample data.
